  "content": "<ul><li data-pid=\"ZPIAFYt7\">其最经典的阐述或许见于<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//notes.andymatuschak.org/zMhuu3pPa6FeNGYn3VfGCar\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">情境学习 - Lave and Wenger</a><sup data-text=\"情境学习 - Lave and Wenger\" data-url=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/696904074\" data-draft-node=\"inline\" data-draft-type=\"reference\" data-numero=\"1\">[1]</sup></li><li data-pid=\"LH5tA6Wt\">其较为温和的表达形式见于<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//notes.andymatuschak.org/z5wZoGy72FafNGd1AHgtghs\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">《反思的实践者》- Donald Schön</a><sup data-text=\"《反思的实践者》- Donald Schön\" data-url=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/1925591199743456768\" data-draft-node=\"inline\" data-draft-type=\"reference\" data-numero=\"2\">[2]</sup></li><li data-pid=\"5KKqvr3-\">相关教育哲学及方法：<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//notes.andymatuschak.org/zWceTLNTjH3DQ7iVpy38ocq\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">建构主义</a><sup data-text=\"建构主义\" data-url=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/1924886118987465823\" data-draft-node=\"inline\" data-draft-type=\"reference\" data-numero=\"3\">[3]</sup>（尤其是激进建构主义）、<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//notes.andymatuschak.org/zHZJPK2nrvAzRstzA6XdmoG\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">锚定教学法</a><sup data-text=\"锚定教学法\" data-url=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/1938891290516390556\" data-draft-node=\"inline\" data-draft-type=\"reference\" data-numero=\"4\">[4]</sup>、<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//notes.andymatuschak.org/zQgeXp15RWkzyiUv9WQsLtA\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">认知学徒制</a><sup data-text=\"认知学徒制\" data-url=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/697335410\" data-draft-node=\"inline\" data-draft-type=\"reference\" data-numero=\"5\">[5]</sup></li><li data-pid=\"vv2Ifzh0\">批判</li><ul><li data-pid=\"c31BnjvL\">来自<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//notes.andymatuschak.org/zFNsXgqNKRmNCM1J9FBeGFP\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">约翰·安德森</a>、雷德、<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//notes.andymatuschak.org/z2khQEBddUwRBv2hXGqNzBq\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">赫伯特·西蒙</a>等认知主义阵营的批判性论战：</li><li data-pid=\"e05AeMTp\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//notes.andymatuschak.org/zNYimPwCAD9FtQV6DTLj377\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Anderson, J. R., Reder, L. M., &amp; Simon, H. A. (1995). Applications and Misapplications of Cognitive Psychology to Mathematics Education</a><sup data-text=\"Anderson, Reder, &amp; Simon (1995)：《认知心理学在数学教育中的正用与误用》\" data-url=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/1936722191761793550\" data-draft-node=\"inline\" data-draft-type=\"reference\" data-numero=\"6\">[6]</sup></li><li data-pid=\"3Ag41Lmo\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//notes.andymatuschak.org/zNwHYafJejVD1CBXNDSLqFS\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Anderson, J. R., Reder, L. M., &amp; Simon, H. A. (1996). Situated Learning and Education. Educational Researcher, 25(4), 5–11</a><sup data-text=\"Anderson, J. R., Reder, L. M., &amp; Simon, H. A. (1996)：《情境学习与教育》\" data-url=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/1936721806074545452\" data-draft-node=\"inline\" data-draft-type=\"reference\" data-numero=\"7\">[7]</sup></li><li data-pid=\"UlDGdFzF\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//notes.andymatuschak.org/zV82AgvZPxBiDMXDW8bFGab\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Greeno, J. G. (1997). On Claims That Answer the Wrong Questions. Educational Researcher, 26(1), 5–17</a><sup data-text=\"Greeno, J. G. (1997)：《论那些答非所问的主张》\" data-url=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/1936721952816476525\" data-draft-node=\"inline\" data-draft-type=\"reference\" data-numero=\"8\">[8]</sup></li><li data-pid=\"sT3TKOTC\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//notes.andymatuschak.org/zQmSCJ2G8pw6ct6nJJR4Hhz\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Anderson, J. R., Reder, L. M., &amp; Simon, H. A. (1997). Situative Versus Cognitive Perspectives: Form Versus Substance. Educational Researcher, 26(1), 18–21</a><sup data-text=\"Anderson, J. R., Reder, L. M., &amp; Simon, H. A. (1997)：《情境视角与认知视角：形式之争还是实质之辩》\" data-url=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/1936722059859308585\" data-draft-node=\"inline\" data-draft-type=\"reference\" data-numero=\"9\">[9]</sup></li><li data-pid=\"BMxZ6rH1\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//notes.andymatuschak.org/zGUDT5KyGRkfacvBktdXj26\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Anderson, J. R., Reder, L. M., Simon, H. A., Ericsson, K. A., &amp; Glaser, R. (1998). Radical Constructivism and Cognitive Psychology. Brookings Papers on Education Policy, 1, 227–278</a><sup data-text=\"Anderson, J. R., Reder, L. M., Simon, H. A., Ericsson, K. A., &amp; Glaser, R. (1998)：《激进建构主义与认知心理学》\" data-url=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/1934572089886642554\" data-draft-node=\"inline\" data-draft-type=\"reference\" data-numero=\"10\">[10]</sup></li><li data-pid=\"h1kQ75tq\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//notes.andymatuschak.org/zUiDqjKiS3udc3wcvcFbcpc\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Kirschner, P. A., Sweller, J., &amp; Clark, R. E. (2006). Why Minimal Guidance During Instruction Does Not Work: An Analysis of the Failure of Constructivist, Discovery, Problem-Based, Experiential, and Inquiry-Based Teaching. Educational Psychologist, 41(2), 75–86</a><sup data-text=\"Kirschner, Sweller, &amp; Clark (2006)：《为什么最小化指导教学是无效的：对建构主义、发现式、问题导向、体验式和探究式教学失败的分析》\" data-url=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/1933460394887868508\" data-draft-node=\"inline\" data-draft-type=\"reference\" data-numero=\"11\">[11]</sup></li></ul><li data-pid=\"jSsUEayv\">观察</li><ul><li data-pid=\"SIrlxwjQ\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//notes.andymatuschak.org/zM1anD1xFyk5aMFM6VXUjUE\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">某些活动（如弹钢琴、烹饪）为有针对性的练习提供了情境化的场所</a><sup data-text=\"某些活动（如弹钢琴、烹饪）为有针对性的练习提供了情境化的场所\" data-url=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/1928197807031968828\" data-draft-node=\"inline\" data-draft-type=\"reference\" data-numero=\"12\">[12]</sup></li><li data-pid=\"M_Rl3x1q\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//notes.andymatuschak.org/z2etsLyP1LJUwNDPCwvRdUG\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">赋能环境着重于环境所赋能的事</a><sup data-text=\"赋能环境着重于环境所赋能的事\" data-url=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/487188240\" data-draft-node=\"inline\" data-draft-type=\"reference\" data-numero=\"13\">[13]</sup></li></ul></ul><h2><br/>链接至本文（已汉化）</h2><ul><li data-pid=\"eIklDCnk\"><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/482949294\" class=\"internal\" target=\"_blank\">赋能环境中的活动直接服务于有内在意义的目的</a></li><li data-pid=\"5APluKls\"><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/487188240\" class=\"internal\" target=\"_blank\">赋能环境着重于环境所赋能的事</a></li><li data-pid=\"R8Roqp8Q\"><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/696904074\" class=\"internal\" target=\"_blank\">情境学习 - Lave and Wenger</a></li><li data-pid=\"VTFP8F0I\"><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/1924886118987465823\" class=\"internal\" target=\"_blank\">建构主义</a></li><li data-pid=\"x0dlM1Gn\"><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/656108634\" class=\"internal\" target=\"_blank\">情景体验可以创造出个人与作者意图的强烈联系</a></li><li data-pid=\"G-Z0kLw8\"><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/628118503\" class=\"internal\" target=\"_blank\">对赋能环境不熟悉的人往往不能完成环境所赋能的事情</a></li><li data-pid=\"F8xuC1Qq\"><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/697335410\" class=\"internal\" target=\"_blank\">认知学徒制</a></li><li data-pid=\"Arhh109P\"><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/1925591199743456768\" class=\"internal\" target=\"_blank\">《反思的实践者》- Donald Schön</a></li><li data-pid=\"jtWELErE\"><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/697566052\" class=\"internal\" target=\"_blank\">超级《启蒙琼林》被嵌入到一个领域中，通过情景体验来引导学习者参与</a></li><li data-pid=\"XGnRzrNX\"><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/696675843\" class=\"internal\" target=\"_blank\">刻意练习不一定非得令人不愉快</a></li><li data-pid=\"7OZYzAQ2\"><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/698045304\" class=\"internal\" target=\"_blank\">《启蒙琼林》是一个脱离情境的视角</a></li><li data-pid=\"bpL3StnM\"><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/1928197807031968828\" class=\"internal\" target=\"_blank\">某些活动（如弹钢琴、烹饪）为有针对性的练习提供了情境化的场所</a></li><li data-pid=\"qAZaC3F6\"><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/1927363022466298690\" class=\"internal\" target=\"_blank\">我该如何调和自己在探究式学习和记忆系统上的观点？</a></li><li data-pid=\"h27vpkkp\"><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/1933460394887868508\" class=\"internal\" target=\"_blank\">Kirschner, Sweller, &amp; Clark (2006)：《为什么最小化指导教学是无效的：对建构主义、发现式、问题导向、体验式和探究式教学失败的分析》</a></li><li data-pid=\"DksS-sjS\"><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/1934572089886642554\" class=\"internal\" target=\"_blank\">Anderson, J. R., Reder, L. M., Simon, H. A., Ericsson, K. A., &amp; Glaser, R. (1998)：《激进建构主义与认知心理学》</a></li><li data-pid=\"4Wd12uGH\"><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/1936721806074545452\" class=\"internal\" target=\"_blank\">Anderson, J. R., Reder, L. M., &amp; Simon, H. A. (1996)：《情境学习与教育》</a></li><li data-pid=\"rWizug4c\"><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/1936721952816476525\" class=\"internal\" target=\"_blank\">Greeno, J. G. (1997)：《论那些答非所问的主张》</a></li><li data-pid=\"SM9MNeCw\"><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/1936722059859308585\" class=\"internal\" target=\"_blank\">Anderson, J. R., Reder, L. M., &amp; Simon, H. A. (1997)：《情境视角与认知视角：形式之争还是实质之辩》</a></li><li data-pid=\"sMux2Z0K\"><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/1936722191761793550\" class=\"internal\" target=\"_blank\">Ander